@startuml Battle Phase — Orchestrator Transition Detail

skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
autonumber

participant BattleCoordinator as Coord
participant BattleOrchestrator as Orch
participant "OldPhase\n(e.g. TurnIdlePhase)" as Old
participant "NewPhase\n(e.g. PlayerTurnPhase)" as New

note over Coord : A phase event fires (e.g. OnUnitReady)

Coord -> Coord : decide next phase
Coord -> Orch : TransitionTo(newPhase)

Orch -> Old : Exit()
Old --> Orch : done

Orch -> Orch : CurrentPhase = newPhase

Orch -> New : Enter()
New --> Orch : done

note over Orch : Each subsequent Tick(dt)\ncalls New.Tick(dt)

@enduml
